marketing: Shell Naturelle S2 Wire Rope Lubricant A is a high performance fully biodegradable grease for use on open gears, wire ropes and cables. This product is formulated with renewable base fluids and contains a select blend of additives to offer corrosion resistance and high load carrying performance. Shell Naturelle S2 Wire Rope Lubricant A offers high resistance to water wash off due to its outstanding adhesion properties.
